" Start selection with Shift + arrows, in whatever mode
" Start selection if not already in visual mode and extend
nnoremap <S-Left>  v<Left>
nnoremap <S-Right> v<Right>
nnoremap <S-Up>    v<Up>
nnoremap <S-Down>  v<Down>
inoremap <S-Left> <Esc><Right>v<Left>
inoremap <S-Right> <Esc><Right>v<Right>
inoremap <S-Up> <Esc><Right>v<Up>
inoremap <S-Down> <Esc><Right>v<Down>
" Extend selection if already in visual mode
vnoremap <S-Left>  <Left>
vnoremap <S-Right> <Right>
vnoremap <S-Up>    <Up>
vnoremap <S-Down>  <Down>

" Similarly, use Alt + Shift + arrows to select by word
