" vnoremap <silent> / :<C-u>call VisualSelection('', '')<CR>?<C-R>=@/<CR><CR>
vnoremap <silent> / y/\V<C-R>=escape(@", '/\')<CR><CR>
" Pressing leader + r triggers replacement of all those patterns
vnoremap <leader>r :<C-u>call VisualSelection('replace', '')<CR>

" Use alt+j/k to move lines up and down
